import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { Component, NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA } from '@angular/core'; import { CircleProgressComponent } from 'ng-circle-progress'; import { ProgressCircleComponent } from '../progress-circle/progress-circle.component'; @Component({ selector: 'app-professorhome', standalone: true, imports: [CommonModule,ProgressCircleComponent], schemas:[NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA], templateUrl: './professorhome.component.html', styleUrl: './professorhome.component.css' }) export class ProfessorhomeComponent { courses = [ { addedDate: '2024-02-15', studentsEnrolled: 25, courseName: 'Angular Basics' }, { addedDate: '2024-02-16', studentsEnrolled: 20, courseName: 'Advanced JavaScript' }, { addedDate: '2024-02-17', studentsEnrolled: 15, courseName: 'Web Development Fundamentals' } ]; isFlipped: boolean = false; progressValue = 50; // Set the initial progress value currentProgressValue: number = 70; // Function to update the progress value updateProgress() { this.progressValue += 10; if (this.progressValue > 100) { this.progressValue = 0; // Reset when reaching 100% } } flipCard() { this.isFlipped = !this.isFlipped; } addCourse() { } }
